metadata.title: Rise of the TMNT Pizza-Shaped Favor Boxes- 8 pcs, Multi-colored, One Size
features: Package includes: 8 pcs. pizza shaped favor boxes with Teenage Mutant Ninja design which measures 1.5in x 4in x 5.25in.

This pizza box looks like a real pizza having the color of the pizza crust, mushrooms and sausages toppings. It has also logo of the "Rise of the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles" on the side of the pizza box.
This box can be filled up with candies and other party treats to be given out to the young ninja warriors who attended the ninja turtle themed party.
Pizza shaped box is made from printed thick paper formed into a box.
description: You can never go wrong if you will include these pizza shaped favor boxes with The Rise of Teenage Ninja Turtle logo when you incude this at your kid's birthday decorations, or simply filled this with sweet treats to be given out to the young ninjas as they went home. These package contains 8 pcs. favor boxes which looks like a real pizza making it more fun and enticing to the eyes of the children.
